{"tid":2393928,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"楊冪過年會否陪「小糯米」團年?　劉丹：問過第二個問題","createTime":"2021-02-04T00:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-04T11:58:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f25bc8bb2df12ea0c0ade28005a656b7d3f85f4f","tid":2393928,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T00:21:00.000Z","msg":"農曆新年即將來臨，TVB處境喜劇《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》一眾演員今天（3日）提早迎春，劉丹表示今天已經是立春，在中國人傳統之間其實等於過年了，他說：「我係北方人，最緊要一家人一齊食飯，同埋最重要有水餃食。」<br />\n<br />\n丹爺一向都非常疼愛孫女「小糯米」是眾所週知的事情，他笑言每年封紅封包給「小糯米」還要比兒子劉愷威還要多，不過丹爺說最開心是兒子能在農曆新年前回香港一起過年：「佢依家返咗嚟隔離緊，一定要隔離。佢過年一定會返，每年都返嚟。」<br />\n<br />\n至於「小糯米」媽媽楊冪長期在內地工作，能不能一起過年，丹爺對這個問題不太想回答：「問第二個問題呀。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210203/433713081772675072270593.jpeg/cvl2tc6yfg-_7yhCvreXsItdV3gGvFfTgCSlKYAkpSk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210203%2F433713081772675072270593.jpeg%2Fcvl2tc6yfg-_7yhCvreXsItdV3gGvFfTgCSlKYAkpSk&h=4d24e550&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40f976fc9be7c8b5e6681dfd4e0c9def2df61717","tid":2393928,"uid":191588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T00:28:28.000Z","msg":"Next question"},{"pid":"c292048757c5404d5d274a5b116866d82797c6b1","tid":2393928,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T00:33:34.000Z","msg":"無可奉告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95208b31d33a2b330bb6edffb59e05fed5078ff5","tid":2393928,"uid":54415,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-04T00:36:10.000Z","msg":"寫文條友大陸嚟架！？紅封包...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a1267ca8bfac2aa8196dec9c142ee8aa14a51e","tid":2393928,"uid":282930,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95208b31d33a2b330bb6edffb59e05fed5078ff5","tid":2393928,"uid":54415,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"